content:
Use the standard console apps for retail banking, wealth management, and commercial banking to streamline client interaction and service management. These console apps have a set of prebuilt functionalities that help your bankers and customer service representatives (CSR) manage their end-to-end service interactions all in one place.

The console apps are available both in the Financial Services Cloud managed package and as a standard feature in your org without installing the managed package. They require enabling the Financial Account Management Standard Objects setting to be accessible.

Here's what you can do with each console app:

* Retail Banking Console: Streamline service interactions for bankers and CSRs.
* Wealth Management Console: Streamline client interaction and service management for wealth managers.
* Commercial Banking Console: Manage complex and changing customer requirements, compliance issues, and the competitive landscape for commercial bankers.

Assign permission sets to users to access these standard console apps. Enable Financial Account Management Standard Objects to set up and use them. You can also customize the prebuilt Lightning pages that come with these console apps.
title: Retail Banking Console App
